{"tid":1889631,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【抗爭心理】請大家永遠記住今晚你有幾開心","createTime":"2020-02-20T17:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T04:09:30.000Z","uid":131691,"like":281,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"d9c6f5516f805e0cbef16ca8e14d2aa14bdbe428","tid":1889631,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"抗爭並唔係一定要用悲慘嚟做燃料，<br />\n用喜悅，用開心都得。<br />\n<br />\n敵人嘅傷亡，爲你今晚帶嚟嘅喜悅<br />\n唔係淨係得今晚！<br />\n我哋一齊繼續努力，<br />\n懷著燦爛嘅笑容咁用火，用刀，送更加多警甴入醫院，入浩園！<br />\n<br />\n請各位香港人永世記住，<br />\n大家要爲呢種開心，呢種興奮，<br />\n繼續爲屬於我哋嘅香港，爲屬於我哋嘅家園時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n請永遠記住今晚你有幾開心。"},{"pid":"726c39be95ca9687a04e7f6b45033a1c3d06ed64","tid":1889631,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1fc5dbd3337a5d55a127932fa91947fd4590a6","tid":1889631,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046f211fe3103b15f117999195f571c1337bbe99","tid":1889631,"uid":294614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:16:46.000Z","msg":"香港人 堅持 今日係721 7個月啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1889630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1889630</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\nP牌仔推唔郁可唔可以幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edda467899c807876290b1ad663fe72749be10fb","tid":1889631,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11ea1a24bcdb6f4455c76cb06ffd19d2d6aa580","tid":1889631,"uid":316420,"like":15,"di